description:
Danny welcomes friend of the show Hannah Brown to dive into QIL Jessica Simpson's new book, OPEN BOOK. The chat is spoiler heavy, so if you haven't read the book but want to, be sure to read before listening! Together they discuss all the tea Queen Jess spilled on the men in her life, her music career, and so much more!
